These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, green
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Color       | azure | green |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
House: craftsman, colonial
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
2. the colonial house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| House   | craftsman | colonial |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
2 different games are played: canasta, go
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Game   | canasta | go |

